                    ]
                  },
                  "dialogue": "Let me show you how to count the total parts. [event:A_count] We count each section in the bar - one, two, three. The bar has [event:69121bb2b9b7bd8c] three equal parts total. That's how we find the [vocab]denominator[/vocab].",
